title: Big Papi 10CD Various Artist Christmas Pack (Oldies and Modern)
description:
A large collection of old standards in Christmas songs, modern hits, and about 4 CD's worth of Christmas classical music.  Plus, one new age CD from Manheimm.

For best results create a playlist and add all your favorite Christmas CD's to it.  Then shuffle play the songs. 

Big Papi accidentally included Louis Armstrong's VA CD in this upload.  It causes no harm but was uploaded as its own CD just the other day :/  Big Papi does not double dip like that.

- Big Papi
